overview:
SonicFiber is your one-stop music shop offering quality musical instruments, from keyboard, guitars, drums, DJ equipment, Lighting devices, cases and recording materials you need.

Conveniently located 15 minutes from NYC, our warehouse can fill orders the same day untol 5pm EST. We carry more than 40 widely-known product lines of musical instruments. Whether you need a new guitar, speakers, DJ gear or anything under the sun, SonicFiber is your one-stop shop for all your musical needs.

Choose from our Big Selection of Goods. If you don’t see what you need in our website, it doesn’t mean we don’t have it. Shoot us an email, join our live chats or give us a quick call to help you find the right item for you. We’ll get you the best deals every time!
